1958;;Further Up the Creek;;British;;Val Guest;;David Tomlinson, Frankie Howerd;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Further_Up_the_Creek;;Navy frigate the "Aristotle" is sold to a Middle Eastern power, and against regulations the ship's bosun tries to make a profit by selling tickets to passengers seeking a luxury cruise. When the Captain discovers what is going on, he attempts to straighten things out.[3]